!! htmlwidgets widget
The widget `htmlwidgets` is to render interactive figures using R package [[htmlwidgets|https://www.htmlwidgets.org/]]. 

!! Syntax
```
<$htmlwidgets type="leaflet" uuid="" data="" filter="" />
```

!! Content and parameters
|Parameter |Type     |Description |h
|type     |required |types of interactive figures. Supported options are `leaflet` and `echarts4r`|
|uuid     |optional |unique id to render figures. A random uuid is generated is missing |
|data     |optional |json object generated by R function `rtiddlywiki::tw_widget` from an htmlwidgets. One of `data` and `filter` have to be specified|
|filter   |optional |filter operators to generate json object as data. See [[Concept]] for details. One of `data` and `filter` have to be specified |
